In our rigorous security protocols, we employ the robust capabilities of the Qualys Cloud Platform to conduct vulnerability assessments for critical components of our infrastructure, including production instances such as pols-prd-bastion. Leveraging Qualys' comprehensive suite of tools and its extensive vulnerability database, we ensure a proactive approach to identifying and addressing potential security risks in real-time. By regularly scanning pols-prd-bastion with Qualys, we maintain a vigilant stance against emerging threats, allowing us to promptly remediate vulnerabilities and fortify our infrastructure's resilience against cyber threats, thus safeguarding the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of our systems and data.
